g.text: Come hang out and meet your fellow Poetic Heroes. We will be raffling 5 Heroes once we reach 5,000 & 10,000 members on Discord as well as 5 Heroes to our most active members on Twitter and Discord

We will make our first Charitable Donations: TOTAL OF 10% OF ALL MINT SALES WILL BE DONATED AS WE ACHIEVE EACH QUARTERLY THRESHOLD. We will also host our first live Slam Poetry Competition on Discord with some exciting prizes for selected participants!

We will make our second Charitable Donations. 10 Heroes airdropped to 10 token holders and/or community members Purchase of Land for the Metaverse to Design the Modern Metaverse History Museum and Performing Arts Center. This is where we will catalog the journey of all our Poetic Heroes and also provide an Open Stage for all aspiring and accomplished artists, singers, poets, writers, and musicians.

Exclusive Poetic Slam Event Featuring Famous Slam Poet...TBA Future Air Drop of the Heroic Poet NFT announced with major financial benefits to all Holders of the Caring Heroes Collection and major future utility for Metaverse! Ownership of the Caring Heroes Collection is your ticket to the many exciting Concerts, Poetic Events, Workshops, that we will regularly host as we transition to the Metaverse! (edited)
